title: Fruity Favorites - Ready-to-Blend Smoothies Order ships & arrives separately from meals. | On-The-Go Goodness
description: Whether you have one for breakfast, a post-workout boost, or a quick snack, our ready-to-blend smoothies are just the treat you need. This assortment features our three fruitiest flavors: Peachy Mango, Banana  Berry, and Acai-Cherry Berry. To enjoy one of these fruit-packed, no-sugar-added blends, all you have to do is blend them with the liquid of your choice (we like whole milk, almond milk, or oat milk) until smooth and enjoy!

*To ensure the highest quality when you receive your smoothies, they will come in a separate box from your meals. Your Ready-to-Blend Smoothie box may arrive a few days after your meal box. Smoothies should be stored frozen.

